scheduler.help.help_ui
Class HelpMenu

java.lang.Object
  mvp.View
      scheduler.help.help_ui.HelpMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer
public class HelpMenu
extends mvp.View

Class HelpMenu is the pulldown menu view of the model class. The HelpMenu widget is a Java JMenu. Anonymous instances of JMenuItem are defined for each item in the menu.
